0.3.0
=====
A) ipmi-sensors: scheme to C conversion
B) bmc-autoconfig: fixed for new bmc-config
C) ipmi-sel: proper trigger output fix
D) Remove Fish
X E) debug dumping for all tools (achu: done)
F) including ipmiconsole + libipmiconsole
G) RPM repackaging
X H) OpenIPMI inband driver suppport (achu: done)

